The '''Baobab Merchant Fleet Complex''' was a docking complex on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Manda/Legends|Manda]].

{{Struct-stub}}

==History==
In [[23 BBY/Legends|23 BBY]], it suffered an explosion from a freighter accident that [[Death/Legends|killed]] over 2,000 employees and grounded 125 Baobab Merchant vessels. It was later determined that [[Lasro Javeq]], the freighter captain, was behind the explosion.

